{
  "total_duration": 527.639,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 11.22,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想象一次 camping trip。傍晚的田野很安静，帐篷搭好了，饭也做好了，大家围着 campfire 讲故事、唱歌。看起来一切都很舒服。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 11.57,
      "end": 21.09,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是到了半夜，帐篷里突然全是水。不是因为帐篷自己坏了，也不只是因为下雨，而是因为他们把帐篷搭在了错误的位置。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 21.44,
      "end": 36.696,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A wet night"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“雨夜”。这课不是鼓励小朋友自己跑到野地里露营，而是一个 outdoor judgment story：在户外，水会往低处走，你要会读懂地面。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 37.045,
      "end": 58.657,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先把安全 bridge 说清楚。现代 camping 通常要在 campsite、park 或学校组织的活动里，有 adults、有 rules，还要看 weather forecast。课文里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "open fire"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "campfire"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，今天也必须有 permission、fire safety 和 adult supervision。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 59.007,
      "end": 68.927,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以今天我们记住一句话：a field may look flat, but rainwater still finds the low path. 田野看起来平，不代表下雨时不会出现水流。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 69.277,
      "end": 87.616,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "故事开始在傍晚："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Late in the afternoon, the boys put up their tent in the middle of a field."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "put up a tent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是搭帐篷。问题也埋在这里："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "in the middle of a field"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，田野中央看起来空，但不一定是安全的帐篷位置。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 87.966,
      "end": 107.054,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "As soon as this was done"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，帐篷刚搭好，他们就"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cooked a meal over an open fire"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。他们都饿了，食物"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "smelled good"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。饭后，他们围着"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "campfire"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "讲故事、唱歌，整个晚上很 warm and happy。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 107.404,
      "end": 128.183,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "过了一会儿，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "some time later it began to rain"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。男孩们累了，所以他们"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "put out the fire"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，把火扑灭，然后"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "crept into their tent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，钻进帐篷。睡袋"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "warm and comfortable"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，他们都"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "slept soundly"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，睡得很沉。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 128.533,
      "end": 151.648,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "半夜，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "two boys woke up and began shouting"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。为什么？"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The tent was full of water!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "大家跳出睡袋，赶紧跑到外面。雨下得很大，他们发现"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a stream had formed in the field"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。那条小溪弯弯曲曲穿过田野，最后"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "flowed right under their tent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 151.998,
      "end": 157.118,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课最重要的问题是：他们为什么会有一个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "wet night"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 157.468,
      "end": 158.882,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为下雨了？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 159.232,
      "end": 172.4,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "下雨只是 trigger，真正的问题是 tent location。雨水聚在低处，临时形成一条"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "stream"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，而他们的帐篷正好在水流经过的位置。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 172.75,
      "end": 177.277,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a stream had formed"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是什么意思？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 177.627,
      "end": 190.611,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "formed"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是出现、形成。heavy rainwater gathers together，then follows lower ground。下大雨时，水聚起来，沿低处走，就可能临时形成一条小溪。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 190.961,
      "end": 197.616,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "wound its way"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "呢？这个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "wound"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“伤口”吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 197.966,
      "end": 214.525,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是。这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "wound"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是动词"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "wind"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的过去式，意思是弯弯曲曲地移动。读的时候不是 injury 的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "wound"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，而是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "wind"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的 past tense。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 214.875,
      "end": 219.295,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "right under"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“正确地在下面”吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 219.645,
      "end": 232.861,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "也不是。这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "right"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 exactly、directly，意思是正好、直接。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "right under their tent"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是正好从他们帐篷底下流过。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 233.211,
      "end": 243.471,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这不是灾难故事，而是一次 outdoor lesson：fun plan 遇到 weather change，natural rule 出现了，preparation suddenly matters。"
        }
      ]
    },
